      },
      "visualKind": "shape",
      "title": "<h1>Lessons Learned – Weekly Retro</h1><h2>🟢 What Went Well</h2><h3>Operations</h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><strong>On-time delivery:</strong> Shipments went out as scheduled without delays</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><strong>Team expansion:</strong> Successfully onboarded additional team members</li></ol><h3>Sales</h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><strong>Goal achievement:</strong> Hit the target goal for the week</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><strong>Effective communication:</strong> Maintained strong communication throughout the team</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><strong>Customer engagement:</strong> Generated valid customer chats</li></ol><h3>Cross-Team</h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><strong>Team morale:</strong> Friday lunch boosted team spirit</li></ol><h2>🔴 What Didn't Go Well</h2><h3>Operations</h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><strong>Sample damage:</strong> Multiple samples arrived chipped or broken</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><strong>Logistics timing:</strong> Could have optimized delivery schedule to arrive sooner</li></ol><h3>Marketing</h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><strong>Content planning gap:</strong> No social media calendar in place, resulting in reactive content creation</li></ol><h3>Sales</h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><strong>Customer satisfaction decline:</strong> CS scores dropped during this period</li></ol><h2>💡 Ideas for Next Time</h2><h3>Marketing</h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><strong>Black Friday campaign:</strong> Plan a comprehensive Black Friday promotion with coupon codes</li></ol><h3>Sales</h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><strong>DM management tools:</strong> Test new software to streamline customer direct message handling</li></ol><h2>🧭 Recommendations for Next Week</h2><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><strong>Create social content calendar:</strong> Build a 2-week content schedule by end of week to prevent reactive posting</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><strong>Review packaging protocol:</strong> Audit shipping procedures to eliminate sample damage in transit</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><strong>CS recovery plan:</strong> Schedule team huddle to identify root causes of score drop and implement quick wins</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><strong>Launch Black Friday planning:</strong> Kickoff campaign strategy meeting with Marketing and Sales by Wednesday</li></ol><h2>🚀 Action Summary</h2><p>The team achieved operational goals and strong collaboration but needs to address quality control in shipping and proactive marketing planning. Top priority is preventing sample damage while building out a structured content calendar ahead of Black Friday.</p>"
    },
